&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span&gt;Senior Clinical Pharmacist&lt;span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a pharmacist with excellent clinical skills to lead a team consisting of a pharmacist, checking technician and dispensers providing outpatient services to Birmingham Children’s Hospital. As well as the opportunity to develop your skills in paediatric pharmacy there will also be opportunity to experience obstetric, gynae. and neonatal pharmacy at our Birmingham Women’s Hospital site. The outpatient service is currently going through an important development phase. As the lead pharmacist reporting to the outpatient services manager you will have the opportunity to contribute to and influence this development.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Essential Attributes:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Pharmacist registered with the GPhC,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Able to act as a role model for patient care &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Able to use leadership skills to engage staff &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Able to understand the complex clinical and social needs of patients &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Able to understand complex clinical situations and to discuss and make recommendations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Able to use a variety of computer software to organise and present information. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Able to work independently, prioritise, set goals and meet deadlines. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Able to identify issues and use own initiative to address them. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Able to maintain standards and accuracy whilst working under pressure.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Able to travel between sites.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Please note, this is not an NHS job but The Medicine Chest is fully integrated within the trust&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;For more information, please contact Ross Flavell- 0121 4721 377,ext 5291&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
